credit.credit-words: His providence hath brought us through Another various year: We all with vows and anthems new Before our God appear.
Sing to the great Jehovah's praise
Our residue of days or hours Thine, wholly Thine, shall be; And all our consecrated powers A sacrifice to Thee.
